premise_source_doc_sentence: It starred Jodie Foster and Kelly McGillis .

It stars Denzel Washington as Detective Keith Frazier , the NYPD 's hostage negotiator ; Clive Owen as Dalton Russell , the mastermind who orchestrates the heist ; and Jodie Foster as Madeleine White , a Manhattan power broker who becomes involved at the request of the bank 's founder , Arthur Case  (  Christopher Plummer  )  , to keep something in his own personal safe deposit box protected from the robbers .
